.chk {  -webkit-appearance: none;  -moz-appearance: none;  appearance: none;  background: transparent;  position: absolute;  visibility: hidden;	}
.chk + label {   background-color: #000000; }
.chk, .chk + label::before {
  font-size: 17px;
  line-height: 18px;
  cursor: pointer;
  vertical-align: middle;
  -webkit-border-radius: 50%;
  -moz-border-radius: 50%;
  -ms-border-radius: 50%;
  -o-border-radius: 50%;
  border-radius: 50%;
  -webkit-user-select: none;
  -moz-user-select: none;
  -ms-user-select: none;
  -o-user-select: none;
  user-select: none;
}
.chk + label::before {
  content: '';
  text-align: center;
  background: #ddd;
  box-shadow: inset 0 0 30px #555;
  display: inline-block;
  pointer-events: none;
  opacity: 1;
  color: black;
  transition: all .3s ease;
  b-order: 3px solid black;
  width: 17px;
  height: 17px;
  margin-right: 5px;
  margin-bottom:2px;
}
.chk:hover + label::before {
  content: '';
  background: #ffffff;
  box-shadow: inset 0 0 30px #aaa;
}
.chk:checked + label::before {
  content: '+';
  box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 15px #5bd75b, 0px 0px 15px #ffffff;
}
.chk:checked:hover + label::before {
  opacity: 1;
}
